00:09:26.919 --> 00:09:33.919
Well, then he puts aside his human concerns and looks to Jehovah for protection.

00:09:33.919 --> 00:09:48.019
In just 40 days more, Nineveh will be overthrown.

00:09:48.019 --> 00:09:53.019
Jehovah, the true God has spoken, this city will be destroyed.

00:09:53.019 --> 00:09:56.019
Nineveh will be overthrown.

00:09:56.019 --> 00:09:59.019
True God will overthrow Nineveh.

00:10:03.759 --> 00:10:09.759
