00:10:09.759 --> 00:10:14.759
Jonah learned a valuable lesson from this experience.

00:10:14.759 --> 00:10:23.759
By recently running away from Nineveh, he chose to trust in himself rather than putting his trust in Jehovah.

00:10:23.759 --> 00:10:30.740
Are you Jonah? Mommy says he saved us.

00:10:30.740 --> 00:10:39.440
