00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:47.039
Jonah learned that without a doubt, Jehovah protects those who trust and obey him.

00:10:47.039 --> 00:10:58.039
If Jehovah has asked you to do something, if he's asked me to do something, if he's leading us, he absolutely will guide us through it.

00:10:58.039 --> 00:11:01.039
Jonah's account proves this.

00:11:02.039 --> 00:11:07.039
Although the Ninevehs were spared because they repented, that's true.

00:11:07.039 --> 00:11:12.039
Aceria later returned to its evil wicked ways.

