00:23:52.130 --> 00:23:55.339
Where?

00:23:55.339 --> 00:23:57.339
I believe that he...

00:23:57.339 --> 00:24:00.339
I know that he will reveal it to me.

00:24:00.339 --> 00:24:02.339
Please, give me time.

00:24:02.339 --> 00:24:08.960
Daniel is not acting on previous experience.

00:24:08.960 --> 00:24:12.960
He hasn't received interpretations of dreams from Jehovah.

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:15.960
Instead, he is acting on faith.

00:24:15.960 --> 00:24:19.960
Faith that he had learned by studying the sacred books of his time.

00:24:19.960 --> 00:24:25.960
These books, likely included the inspired writings of Moses and David Solomon,

00:24:25.960 --> 00:24:28.960
Isaiah, Jeremiah, and other prophets.

00:24:28.960 --> 00:24:31.960
Oh, we can only imagine Daniel.

00:24:31.960 --> 00:24:33.960
Pouring over these scrolls,

00:24:33.960 --> 00:24:39.960
opening up his heart to Jehovah, begging Jehovah to give him wisdom and understanding.

00:24:39.960 --> 00:24:41.960
He loved it.

00:24:41.960 --> 00:24:45.960
And there's no doubt that as Daniel studied these accounts,

00:24:45.960 --> 00:24:47.960
his faith was strengthened,

00:24:47.960 --> 00:24:51.960
and his bond with Jehovah drew even closer.

00:24:51.960 --> 00:24:55.960
But even though Daniel knew nothing of King Nebuchadnezzar's dream,

00:24:55.960 --> 00:25:01.960
he was fully convinced that Jehovah would reveal the dream and its interpretation

00:25:01.960 --> 00:25:04.960
and prove to be Daniel's salvation.

00:25:04.960 --> 00:25:09.960
Do we know exactly which accounts Daniel was able to draw from at this time?

00:25:09.960 --> 00:25:12.960
It's impossible to say for a certainty.

00:25:12.960 --> 00:25:15.960
But we do know he had access to the books.

00:25:15.960 --> 00:25:18.960
He references the prophecies of Jeremiah.

00:25:18.960 --> 00:25:23.960
Daniel could see how Jehovah blessed faithful, obedient men in the past.

00:25:23.960 --> 00:25:26.960
So by asking Nebuchadnezzar for time,

00:25:26.960 --> 00:25:29.960
he wasn't looking to buy himself another day of life.

00:25:29.960 --> 00:25:37.619
He was allowing Jehovah to reward his faith by revealing the dream to him.

00:25:37.619 --> 00:25:40.619
Daniel strikes a balance here,

00:25:40.619 --> 00:25:45.619
although he is confident that Jehovah will reveal the dream to him.

00:25:45.619 --> 00:25:49.619
He isn't casual in the way he handled the situation.

00:25:49.619 --> 00:25:53.619
He did what any God-fearing man would do here.

00:25:53.619 --> 00:25:57.619
He approached Jehovah in prayer.

00:25:57.619 --> 00:26:01.619
Oh, Jehovah, surely you didn't bring us here just to die.

00:26:02.619 --> 00:26:05.619
What will people say?

00:26:05.619 --> 00:26:12.619
We told them that you are the God of the heavens, the only God who can reveal secrets.

00:26:12.619 --> 00:26:17.119
Please, vindicate yourself.

00:26:17.119 --> 00:27:00.990
The man from the axiles of Judah who can make known the interpretation to the king.

00:27:00.990 --> 00:27:05.009
I know who he is.

00:27:05.009 --> 00:27:09.009
Can you really make known to me the dream that I saw and its interpretation?

00:27:21.619 --> 00:27:27.500
There is a God in the heavens who is a revealer of secrets.

00:27:27.500 --> 00:27:36.450
And he has made known to King Nebuchadnezzar what is to happen in the final part of the days.

00:27:36.450 --> 00:27:38.450
This is your dream.

00:27:38.450 --> 00:27:47.809
You saw an immense image.

00:27:47.809 --> 00:28:02.940
That image was standing in front of you.

00:28:02.940 --> 00:28:05.940
You yourself are the head of God.

00:28:05.940 --> 00:28:13.220
After you, another kingdom will rise and fear you to you.

00:28:13.220 --> 00:28:15.220
Then another kingdom.

00:28:15.220 --> 00:28:20.220
A third one of copper that will rule over the whole earth.

00:28:20.220 --> 00:28:25.220
As for the fourth kingdom, it will be strong like iron.

00:28:25.220 --> 00:28:30.140
The kingdom will be divided.

00:28:30.140 --> 00:28:35.140
And as the toes of the feet were partly of iron and partly of clay,

00:28:35.140 --> 00:28:40.140
so the kingdom will be partly strong and partly fragile.

00:28:40.140 --> 00:28:48.440
This took a tremendous amount of faith and courage on the part of Daniel.

00:28:49.440 --> 00:28:52.440
Now we may find our peace threatened.

00:28:52.440 --> 00:28:55.440
Our very lives might be on the line.

00:28:55.440 --> 00:28:59.440
In that moment, we can turn to Jehovah God in prayer,

00:28:59.440 --> 00:29:04.440
opening up our hearts, confident that he will support us.

00:29:04.440 --> 00:29:10.440
Like both Daniel and Jonah, we've been given an assignment to proclaim a message.

00:29:10.440 --> 00:29:17.440
This requires courage to speak out boldly concerning Jehovah's judgments against those who oppose his sovereignty.

00:29:18.440 --> 00:29:25.440
Both of these prophets are excellent examples of Jehovah backing those who trust in him.

00:29:25.440 --> 00:29:30.440
Jehovah will always be with us as long as we have faith in him.

00:29:30.440 --> 00:29:35.440
When we face situations that seem impossible as in the case with Hezekiah,

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:41.440
we have the ability to tap into the most powerful force there is.

00:29:41.440 --> 00:29:44.440
As this system comes to a close,

00:29:44.440 --> 00:29:51.440
we will find ourselves in situations that test our courage and threaten our peace.

00:29:51.440 --> 00:29:55.440
We will have to stand up for pure worship, just like Josiah,

00:29:55.440 --> 00:29:57.440
and this will be unpopular.

00:29:57.440 --> 00:30:02.440
But with Jehovah on our side, we can face those situations with confidence.

00:30:02.440 --> 00:30:06.440
He's all powerful, and he's going to help us through it.

00:30:06.440 --> 00:30:09.440
Now here's the interesting thing.

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:16.440
Some of the prophecies that Daniel recorded applied not only to the future of the Babylonian Empire,

00:30:16.440 --> 00:30:23.440
but also outline world events to our day and beyond.

00:30:23.440 --> 00:30:30.440
And these events are being fulfilled right before our very eyes.
